OL,3,CJersey to face rising energy bills in
OL,4,C2026
OL,6,FThe 2.5% tariff increase will come
OL,7,Finto force in Jersey on 1 March 2026.
OL,9,FThe hike is forecast to add an extra
OL,10,F#60 per year to household bills, or
OL,11,Fjust over #1 per week.
OL,13,FThe figure is based on the average all-
OL,14,Felectric household, which uses around
OL,15,F10,000 units of electricity annually.
