OL,3,CJersey to face rising energy bills in
OL,4,C2026
OL,6,FJersey Electricity (JE) states that
OL,7,Fthe tariff rise is due to "cost-of-
OL,8,Fliving" pressures and "operational
OL,9,Fcosts", with the company investing
OL,10,F#180 million over five years in
OL,11,Finfrastructure development.
OL,13,FIn a statement, the company's Chief
OL,14,FExecutive, Chris Ambler, said he
OL,15,Funderstands the announcement may come
OL,16,Fas "unwanted" news to islanders.
OL,18,FHe said: "We've worked hard to keep
OL,19,Fthis increase as low as possible.
