OL,3,CJersey to face rising energy bills in
OL,4,C2026
OL,6,FThe JE chief said the island's
OL,7,Felectricity prices will remain
OL,8,Fconsiderably lower than rates in
OL,9,FEurope and the other Channel Islands.
OL,11,FMr Ambler continued: "This increase
OL,12,Freflects a pricing strategy that
OL,13,Fcontinues to benchmark well for our
OL,14,Fcommunity".
OL,16,FThe statement also added that JE is
OL,17,Fmoving forward with supply contract
OL,18,Fnegotiations.
