OL,3,CJersey to face rising energy bills in
OL,4,C2026
OL,6,FMr Ambler said: "While there will be
OL,7,Fsome structural changes to the new
OL,8,Fcontract, we are confident that this
OL,9,Fnew framework will continue to deliver
OL,10,Fcompetitively priced power and
OL,11,Fcontinued good outcomes for consumers."
OL,13,FJE defended an earlier increase in its
OL,14,Fprices at the start of this year, when
OL,15,Ftariffs went up by 7.5% and was
OL,16,Festimated to add #2 per week to the
OL,17,Faverage domestic electricity bill of
OL,18,F#1,400 per year.
